Module  : Compress Javascript using Packer
Version : 1.0.0
Author  : Maurice Makaay

This module compresses the Phorum Javascript code using Dean Edwards'
JavaScript Packer algorithm. This reduces bandwidth usage and speeds up the
JavaScript code.

For more information see:

Dean Edwards' website - http://dean.edwards.name/packer/
PHP implementation - http://dean.edwards.name/packer/

Install:
--------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "compress_packer" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "Compress Javascript using Packer".

